{"tid":1660655,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU中斷工作神隱3天…　韓媒親曝「她一直守著靈堂陪伴雪莉」！","createTime":"2019-10-17T15:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T19:29:12.000Z","uid":34643,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"68c74cdf5d00c68e4f80248e2cfe6da19ba477b3","tid":1660655,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"記者張筱涵／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n韓星雪莉出殯儀式在17日舉行，其中從2011年就相識的IU也在好友去世當天登上熱搜，不只因為她們的好感情，更因為她曾經想著對方寫出一首浪漫曲子《桃子》，而她雖然這3天都沒有對外發聲，但其實一直守著靈堂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4445/4445024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4445%2F4445024.jpg&h=8442cc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU和雪莉感情要好。（圖／翻攝自雪莉IG）<br />\n<br />\n據韓媒《STARNEWS》報導，雪莉的靈堂設置好後，除了f(x)成員特別調節行程抵韓弔唁，家人和其他好友也都有出席，特別是一直以來就因為要好感情廣為人知的IU，一直守著靈堂陪伴著故人雪莉。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，IU和雪莉2011年透過擔任《人氣歌謠》主持人認識，當年分別只有18、19歲的兩個小女孩一拍即合，於公於私都是最佳夥伴和談心好友。在IU推出《二十歲的春天》前就一直跟對方說「很快就會有為妳寫的歌問世」，雪莉一看到《桃子》就興奮傳訊：「就是這首歌對吧？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4445/4445033.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4445%2F4445033.jpg&h=99fcd12f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪莉上節目開心說道IU為了她寫首歌。（圖／翻攝自MBCentertainment YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n雪莉開心透露IU常常看著她說「雪莉呀～妳怎麼這麼白～怎麼身高這麼高～髮質怎麼這麼好呀」，每次聽到的都只有稱讚，甚至還被對方選為「如果是男生會想交往的對象」，要好感情維持至今也有8年之久，不只友情客串《德魯納酒店》，對方10周年演唱會也是一定到場，IG上也常能看到她開心炫耀IU來家裡做的料理。<br />\n<br />\nIU原本預計在11月1日以新專輯《LOVE POEM》回歸，碰上情同姊妹的雪莉離世決定中斷原定的新專輯行程，雖然沒有出面發聲或透過社群平台發文，但默默守護著靈堂送雪莉最後一程，就是她最大最深的溫柔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4445/d4445071.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4445%2Fd4445071.jpg&h=034c48c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲雪莉參加IU十周年演唱會，友情客串《德魯納酒店》。（圖／翻攝自雪莉IG）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4445/d4445074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4445%2Fd4445074.jpg&h=4bac46a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4445/d4445073.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4445%2Fd4445073.jpg&h=41694fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4445/d4445070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4445%2Fd4445070.jpg&h=cfe6485c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲IU常做菜給雪莉吃。（圖／翻攝自雪莉IG）"},{"pid":"3770ee64c4bf801c18a79fbcd4f0845500d44257","tid":1660655,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:32:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"672e33ab22589517d8aeb5ecbc94dfe26f33b98e","tid":1660655,"uid":34643,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://file6.instiz.net/data/cached_img/upload/2016/08/26/23/d6e8cd1fc5b19d137329c8163db49f80.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile6.instiz.net%2Fdata%2Fcached_img%2Fupload%2F2016%2F08%2F26%2F23%2Fd6e8cd1fc5b19d137329c8163db49f80.gif&h=955afa78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3531de5ba5d8c73891b92d1453f8d1598c016cae","tid":1660655,"uid":34643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://file6.instiz.net/data/cached_img/upload/2016/08/26/23/bbcd9aa54e29738e5ec5b02e3aa87ea9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile6.instiz.net%2Fdata%2Fcached_img%2Fupload%2F2016%2F08%2F26%2F23%2Fbbcd9aa54e29738e5ec5b02e3aa87ea9.gif&h=65b7f37a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac0884aa32672544a53bea19fb7e0d58e9cde1b9","tid":1660655,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T15:33:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /